\c 140
\s Dhavhidhi anonyengetera kuti arwirwe pavavengi vake \d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Nadirwu irueiwJeakhaoivphaa., p Ndichengetei pamunhu anehasha;
\v 2 Ivo, vanofunga zvakaipa mumwoyo yavo; Vanogara vachimutsa kurwa.
\v 3 Vakarodza rurimi rwavo senyoka; Uturu hwechiva huri pasi pemiromo yavo.
\v 4 Ndichengetei, Jehovha, pamaoko owakaipa; Ndichengetei pamunhu anomanikidza; Vanofunga mano okugumburisa tsoka dzangu.
\v 5 Vanozvikudza vakandivanzira musungo namabote; Vakadzika mumbure parutivi rwenzira, Vakanditeyera rugombe.
\v 6 Ndakati kuna Jehovha, Mwari wangu; "
\s Teererai, Jehovha, munzwe izwi rokukumbira kwangu.
\p
\v 7 Mwari Ishe, ndimi simba rokuponeswa kwangu,
